Invocation Name: fauna facts
des:
This skill will tell you some fun facts about Fauna which you might not know. 
You can open this skill by using the phrase: "Alexa, open fauna facts" and then to know some fun facts you can say utterances like: "tell me a fauna fact", "tell a fauna fact", "tell fauna fact", "fauna fact" or "fact". And Thus you get to know some interesting fun facts.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
